rest_of_day_open: It should be very busy, but interesting! I went back to school today so there likely won't be a lot of schoolwork so much as there will be a lot of trying to get mentally ready. It's also my dad's and my sister's birthdays so I will be making a huge, special dinner for the two of them.
critical_positive: My partner and I had a lot of similar views, which does help. He wasn't afraid to dive in deep with some tougher topics, which makes for rich conversation. However, before he did, he sort of "felt me out" to try to get an idea of where I was at.
critical_negative: There were a few times where I asked my partner a question and it seemed like he either did not process it or he ignored it. It did make me feel a little awkward at first, but I got used to it. I still think we had a productive conversation!

critical_positive: I think it was a interesting conversation,she was really nice person.We talked about different issues,she is very educated person that goes to school and wants to do something with her life.It was a great experience for me,i don't really speak to many white people in my community.Great person to speak to.
